<a href="/wiki/Bohori%C4%8D_alphabet" title="Bohorič alphabet">Bohoričica</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="/wiki/Dajnko_alphabet" title="Dajnko alphabet">Dajnčica</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="/wiki/Metelko_alphabet" title="Metelko alphabet">Metelčica</a><br />
<a href="/wiki/Arebica" title="Arebica">Arebica</a>&#160;<span style="font-weight:bold;">·</span>  <a href="/wiki/Bosnian_Cyrillic" title="Bosnian Cyrillic">Bosnian Cyrillic</a><br />
